snippet.title: Outbreak Island - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Take a tour of an abandoned diner in search of food, fight off creepy enemies, and see how to spend your time hunting for food, medical supplies, and more in the upcoming open-world sandbox survival horror game Outbreak Island.
